title: [Foothills, Trail]
description: Running east-west across the flat land, the road leads towards a distant group of buildings to the east.  To the north, the peak of a mountain can be seen silhouetted against the night sky, giving this area a striking view.

Running east-west across the flat land, the road leads towards a distant group of buildings to the east.  To the north, the peak of a snow-capped mountain can be seen reaching into the clouds, giving this area a striking view.
